    <section class="square-carousel-landscape grey-mid" aria-labelledby="carousel-heading">
      <div class="article_wrapper square-landscape-heading-container">
                <h3>
          2024 General election
        </h3>
                        <p>
          <p>With a general election on the way, it’s time to send a strong message to the next UK government. Nature and climate must be a crucial part of the agenda.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>All your local candidates need to hear from you! Let them know that restoring our world gets your vote.&nbsp;</p><p>We have some useful resources to help you below.&nbsp;</p>
        </p>
              </div>

