    <section class="square-carousel-landscape " aria-labelledby="carousel-heading">
      <div class="article_wrapper square-landscape-heading-container">
                <h3>
          Stop the destruction of nature posters
        </h3>
                        <p>
          <p>With a general election on the way, it’s time to send a strong message to all party candidates campaigning in your area: Nature and climate must be a crucial part of the agenda for the next UK government.</p><p>Are you worried about climate change and loss of nature? Do you ever wonder why politicians don’t talk about it enough? One reason is that politicians don’t realise how important climate and nature are to the people who vote for them.&nbsp;</p><p>You can help change that. By downloading and putting up one of these posters in your window or local community you are letting all candidates know that restoring our world gets your vote.&nbsp;</p><p>Below are different options from full colour, colour in at home and with and without the WWF-UK logo.&nbsp;</p>
        </p>
              </div>

