  <section id="using-your-political-power" class="slider-slice_container paragraph-container">
    <section class="square-carousel-landscape " aria-labelledby="carousel-heading">
      <div class="article_wrapper square-landscape-heading-container">
                <h3>
          Using your political power
        </h3>
                        <p>
          <p>Your elected representatives can act for nature in your local area, nationally and internationally. It’s their job to prioritise what’s important to the people they represent – you!&nbsp;</p>
        </p>
              </div>

