      <div class="heading-container">
                <h3>
          Be inspired by...
        </h3>
              </div>
      <div class="splide">
        <div class="splide__track">
          <ul class="splide__list">
                                                                                                <li class="splide__slide" data-link-url="https://www.avivacommunityfund.co.uk/save-our-wild-isles" data-link-text="Explore projects">
                <figure>
                  <div class="caption-link-bg">
                    <figcaption>
                                                                                          <h4>Save Our Wild Isles Community Fund</h4>
                                            <p>From creating community gardens and replanting wildflower meadows, to protecting local wildlife and promoting community connection to nature, these community groups are taking action and have been supported by the Save Our Wild Isles Community Fund.&nbsp;</p>
                    </figcaption>
                                          <div class="btn-wrap">
                        <div class="btn-wrap--item">
                          <a href="https://www.avivacommunityfund.co.uk/save-our-wild-isles" class="btn btn--white">
