  <section id="using-your-spending-power" class="slider-slice_container paragraph-container">
    <section class="square-carousel-landscape " aria-labelledby="carousel-heading">
      <div class="article_wrapper square-landscape-heading-container">
                <h3>
          Using your spending power
        </h3>
                        <p>
          <p><span lang="EN-GB">The things we buy and the businesses we buy them from can have a huge impact on nature – for good or bad. Together, we have the power to put pressure on businesses that destroy nature and support the ones that are doing the right thing.</span><span>&nbsp;</span></p>
        </p>
              </div>

